    "# Bayes Rule"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$ P(A \\cap B) = P(B|A)*P(A) $"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$ P(B|A) = \\frac{P(A and B)}{P(A)} $"
   ]
  },
  {
   "cell_type": "markdown",
   "metadata": {},
   "source": [
    "$ P(first=red \\cap second =red) = P(second=red \\mid first = red) * P(first= red) = 2/ 4 * 3 /5 = 6/20 = 3/10 $"
